<br>
Quietly, the mare moved along the path thru the trees. Still the light chant could be heard from Hippolyte's lips.  Softly she ran finger tips along her sacred golden belt and whispered, &quot;Father be with me.&quot;  Then her fingertips ran across the tattoo of a peacock feather upon her arm, &quot;Grandmother be with me.&quot;  Then the finger tips ran up to rest upon her breast above her leather bodice, &quot;Mother be with me.&quot;  Then her words again resummed to those ancient words of prayer.<br>
